im figured out . we normally do him with 30 or so and maybe 1 or 2 deaths . also you are going to want to use youre aoe hael word of vigor in this fight . just have clerics make sure to inform there groups to stay withing range of heal and you should be set . make sure everyone has rune and spellshield and you should be set . a ntov / primal equipped guild could probly handle him with 18 - 24 ppl easy . <br>
